   "source": [
    "# Gallery\n",
    "\n",
    "The following examples are a bit more involved and showcase the kind of drawings that can be done with Tesserax in the academic domain.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Sorting"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "6e44ca26",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
